Sony has announced that all gamers, including current PlayStation Plus members, can receive 25% off a 12-month PlayStation Plus membership. The offer is available on the PlayStation Store and will end at 12:00 on 23 March. The offer will also be available at participating retailers in select markets. Sony said there are currently over 31.5 million PlayStation Plus paid members around the world, who receive online multiplayer and free game benefits as part of their subscription.